             <span class="fs-5 mb-2">What is Healthy Fit Raho Basic BodyCheckup </span> 
             <p style="text-align:justify;">The Healthy Fit Raho Basic BodyCheckup  includes an array of tests available at an affordable price in delhi ncr with healthynation labs. This routine checkup is designed to examine your overall well-being and identify any potential health issues or illnesses early on. This early detection allows your doctor to suggest lifestyle adjustments or prescribe medications to manage your conditions and develop a holistic treatment plan.</p>
             <p class="mb-2" style="text-align: justify;">A Healthy Fit Raho Basic BodyCheckup, including a complete blood count (CBC) test, liver function test (LFT), kidney function test (KFT), diabetes screening, thyroid profile, lipid profile, calcium test, and urine analysis among others. This package is a part of our ‘premium range’ of diagnostic tests and can be ordered once every 6 to 12 months or as recommended by your doctor.</p>
             <span class="fs-5">What does Healthy Fit Raho Basic BodyCheckup with  measure?</span>
             
             <hr>
             <p style="text-align: justify;">The Healthy Fit Raho Basic BodyCheckup with helps detect various health conditions at an early stage thereby minimizing possible complications. This package includes about 71 tests including lipid profile, liver function, kidney function, thyroid profile, blood count, diabetes screening, calcium, iron, etc.</p>
        
        <a class="" data-bs-toggle="collapse" href="#cbc" role="button" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseExample">
          <div class="details d-inline-flex border-bottom pt-2 pb-2">
            <span>CBC (Complete Blood Count)</span>
            <i class="fas fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
